---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="V-PACK Batarya Sistemi - Voltz Power Tools | Tek Platform, Sınırsız Güç"
  description="Voltz V-PACK batarya sistemi ile tek batarya, tüm aletler. 20V ve 16.8V seçenekleriyle 13+ ürünle uyumlu modüler batarya ekosistemi."
  keywords="v-pack batarya, modüler batarya sistemi, akülü alet bataryası, voltz batarya, 20V batarya, 16.8V batarya, power tools battery"
>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="vpack-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vpack-hero-inner">
        <span class="section-tag">V-PACK EKOSİSTEMİ</span>
        <h1>V-PACK<br>Batarya <span class="text-green">Sistemi</span></h1>
        <p class="vpack-hero-desc">Tek batarya platformu, tüm Voltz aletleri. Geleceğin güç çözümü ile maksimum verimlilik ve maliyet tasarrufu.</p>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <span class="hero-stat-value">20V</span>
            <span class="hero-stat-label">Profesyonel Seri</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <span class="hero-stat-value">16.8V</span>
            <span class="hero-stat-label">Kompakt Seri</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stat-divider"></div>
          <div class="hero-stat">
            <span class="hero-stat-value">13+</span>
            <span class="hero-stat-label">Uyumlu Ürün</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section class="how-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="how-header">
        <span class="section-tag">NASIL ÇALIŞIR</span>
        <h2>Üç Adımda <span class="text-green">Başlayın</span></h2>
        <p class="how-subtitle">V-PACK sistemi ile başlamak bu kadar kolay.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="6" width="22" height="12" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="23" y1="13" x2="23" y2="11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Bataryanızı Seçin</h3>
          <p>20V Profesyonel veya 16.8V Kompakt seriden ihtiyacınıza uygun bataryayı seçin.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Şarj Edin</h3>
          <p>Hızlı şarj cihazı ile kısa sürede tam güce ulaşın. Akıllı şarj koruması dahil.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Herhangi Bir Aletle Kullanın</h3>
          <p>Aynı bataryayı tüm uyumlu Voltz aletlerinde takıp kullanın. Ekstra batarya gereksiz.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compatible Products Section -->
  <section class="compatible-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="compatible-header">
        <span class="section-tag">UYUMLU ÜRÜNLER</span>
        <h2>Geniş <span class="text-green">Ürün Yelpazesi</span></h2>
        <p class="compatible-subtitle">V-PACK batarya sistemi ile uyumlu tüm Voltz el aletleri.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="compatible-grid">
        <div class="compat-card">
          <div class="compat-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Matkaplar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="compat-card">
          <div class="compat-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Tornavidalar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="compat-card">
          <div class="compat-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Taşlama</span>
        </div>
        <div class="compat-card">
          <div class="compat-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12h5l2-9 6 18 2-9h5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Darbeli Matkaplar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="compat-card">
          <div class="compat-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"/><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"/><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Dekupaj Testere</span>
        </div>
        <div class="compat-card">
          <div class="compat-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span>Diğer Aletler</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="compatible-cta">
        <a href="/products" class="btn-outline">
          TÜM ÜRÜNLERİ GÖR
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="benefits-header">
        <span class="section-tag">AVANTAJLAR</span>
        <h2>Neden <span class="text-green">V-PACK</span>?</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Maliyet Tasarrufu</h3>
          <p>Tek batarya ile tüm aletlerinizi çalıştırarak batarya maliyetlerini %70'e kadar azaltın.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Kolay Kullanım</h3>
          <p>Aletler arası batarya geçişi saniyeler içinde. Tek tık ile tak-çıkar mekanizması.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="6" width="22" height="12" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="23" y1="13" x2="23" y2="11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Uzun Ömür</h3>
          <p>5000+ şarj döngüsü garantili Li-ion hücreler. Akıllı BMS ile aşırı şarj/deşarj koruması.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"/><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"/><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Geniş Ürün Yelpazesi</h3>
          <p>13'ten fazla ürünle uyumlu ve sürekli büyüyen ekosistem. Yeni ürünler otomatik uyumlu.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <div class="cta-inner">
          <h2>V-PACK Ekosistemine Geçin</h2>
          <p>Profesyonel iş akışınızı sadeleştirin, maliyetlerinizi düşürün. Voltz V-PACK ile gücü keşfedin.</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/products" class="btn-primary">
              ÜRÜNLERİ KEŞFET
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">İLETİŞİME GEÇİN</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand"><img src="/img/logo/footer-logo.svg" alt="Voltz Power Tools" class="footer-logo"><p>Profesyonel el aletlerinde güvenin adresi.</p></div>
        <div class="footer-links"><h4>Sayfalar</h4><a href="/">Anasayfa</a><a href="/about">Hakkımızda</a><a href="/products">Ürünlerimiz</a><a href="/contact">İletişim</a></div>
        <div class="footer-links"><h4>Ürünler</h4><a href="/products">Matkaplar</a><a href="/products">Tornavidalar</a><a href="/products">Taşlama</a><a href="/v-pack">V-PACK Sistem</a></div>
        <div class="footer-contact-col"><h4>İletişim</h4><p>Teknoloji Caddesi No: 123<br>Sanayi Mahallesi, İstanbul</p><a href="mailto:info@voltzpowertools.com">info@voltzpowertools.com</a><a href="tel:+902123456789">+90 212 345 67 89</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom"><p>&copy; 2025 Voltz Power Tools. Tüm hakları saklıdır.</p><div class="footer-social"><a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg></a><a href="#" aria-label="Instagram"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/></svg></a></div></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  .text-green { color: var(--green); }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    color: var(--green-dark);
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Semibold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* ========== HERO ========== */
  .vpack-hero {
    padding: 80px 0 72px;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vpack-hero-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .vpack-hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .vpack-hero-desc {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 32px 48px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .hero-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-stat-value {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .hero-stat-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .hero-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* ========== HOW IT WORKS ========== */
  .how-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .how-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .how-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .how-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .how-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .how-step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: all var(--transition);
    position: relative;
  }

  .how-step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-color: var(--green);
  }

  .step-number {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 48px;
    color: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.15);
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--green);
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
  }

  .how-step h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .how-step p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  /* ========== COMPATIBLE PRODUCTS ========== */
  .compatible-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }

  .compatible-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .compatible-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .compatible-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .compatible-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .compat-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 32px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }

  .compat-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--green);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .compat-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.08);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--green);
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }

  .compat-card span {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Semibold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--dark);
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
  }

  .compatible-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--green);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-green);
  }

  .btn-outline svg {
    transition: transform var(--transition);
  }

  .btn-outline:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  /* ========== BENEFITS ========== */
  .benefits-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .benefits-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .benefits-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }

  .benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-color: var(--green);
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
